        "id": 1003003
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-10T11:43:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, line 496 clears the buffered per-fetch state, but the motivation for this patch is to remove the function-static state entirely. The change makes that temporary state instance-scoped, with explicit reset points, so the behavior is easier to reason about and no longer depends on hidden static locals.",
      "parentUuid": "c8f01b6f_cb386641",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 496,
        "startChar": 7,
        "endLine": 496,
