      "writtenOn": "2026-07-10T11:43:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We cannot use mergedHostPdrs directly there because it is cleared by resetPDRProcessingState(). The local variable preserves the current-cycle result so we can still decide whether to send the PDR repository changed event afterward.",
